{"tid":97430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懶理Trump行政命令 這些庇護城市力保移民 ！！","createTime":"2017-01-27T15:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T03:05:12.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae1b96d7f464a4ab4a5eef768ca080aedbf7076b","tid":97430,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>不甩川普行政命令　這些「庇護城市」力保移民</strong><br />\n2017年01月26日12:08<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170126/640_681b5d87c3443fbb81242ce2efefa5b9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170126%2F640_681b5d87c3443fbb81242ce2efefa5b9.jpg&h=ed09667b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐新社<br />\n<br />\n美國總統川普簽署行政命令，確定要蓋美墨邊界城牆，加強邊境管理。此外川普同時也簽署取消聯邦政府對「庇護城市」（sanctuary cities）的資助計畫。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的「庇護城市」其實只是一個行政概念，並沒有正式的定義，泛指<span style=\"color: red;\">市府當局拒絕向聯邦政府提供非法入境者的名單，以免遭聯邦政府遣返。</span>諸如紐約、洛杉磯、西雅圖、費城、舊金山，及芝加哥等城市都屬於庇護城市。簽署這項命令，即新政府將停止向這些城市提供聯邦撥款。<br />\n<br />\n對此，紐約市長白思豪（Bill de Blasio）痛批，簽署這項命令「不道德」，並誓言反抗到底：「我們不會遣返遵守法令的紐約客，也不會拆散這些家庭。」強調市府不會讓警方將名單送到移民局：「白宮簽署這項命令，不會改變紐約人的價值觀，也不會改變市政府保護人民的方式，不會改變我們如何執法」。<br />\n<br />\n位在西岸的民主黨大票倉加州，轄下數個城市如<strong>洛杉磯、舊金山</strong>也都被視為庇護城市。舊金山市長李孟賢 （Ed Lee）同樣也發表談話，強調不會讓市區內的移民「生活在恐懼之中」，將維持市府一貫的、施行27年的庇護城市傳統。<br />\n<br />\n李孟賢：「我們維護庇護城市政策，要讓每個人感到有安全感，並得以利用應得的資源，包括教育及醫療...我有義務要讓整個市維持團結、茁壯，犯罪和疾病不會區分是否有（身份證明）文件」。<br />\n<br />\n（林孝儒／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170126/1044013/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170126%2F1044013%2F&d=k9ZiUbGtGu0WCTuOQXTcB0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=6f47e019\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170126/1044013/</a>"},{"pid":"394bb857896c29209402458ee073e0d8d66357d8","tid":97430,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:48:58.000Z","msg":"啲美國佬真係幾撚on9 移民同非法入境者都唔識分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1acfbcc14727cbdfaa6013739a4600907b882c5","tid":97430,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:49:40.000Z","msg":"😨😨😨<br />\n西隙鳩利"},{"pid":"ae0b24b7b83eff82f3ff30b1566d9c6ed4bb2c1e","tid":97430,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68334063cbc68c26787fc2980bc1d4ea7cd824a","tid":97430,"uid":25641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e08ca74c00103597b403eb318d8be842a9730c0a","tid":97430,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T16:10:58.000Z","msg":"$"},{"pid":"409596cf8f419763b6327f265f9a525a16a2a69c","tid":97430,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fada2091bb63c28f04462c6c910977f55598dc14","tid":97430,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:23:24.000Z","msg":"包庇偷渡入境。 影響本地人生格"},{"pid":"126716f49bb9de7cd4dabeab82c852ee14c6623b","tid":97430,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:44:31.000Z","msg":"果d市長純為選票<br />\n<br />\n香港偽政府官員加一堆有米離地香港人何嘗唔係一樣？"},{"pid":"18282a85663b48bb90a113d2f3275032b2fabcdc","tid":97430,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:56:27.000Z","msg":"左膠當道"},{"pid":"fd753eb95cb5a435878348af98673dc10ed61aeb","tid":97430,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:57:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就黎內戰？<img src=\"/assets/faces